title: Portrait Photography Workshop
description: A hands-on workshop on portrait photography led by expert photographer Mr. Mohammad Shabeb. An opportunity to learn and practice portrait photography techniques.

title: Landscape Photography Excursion
description: Join us for a day trip to capture the beauty of natural landscapes. Perfect for enthusiasts looking to improve their outdoor photography skills.

title: Street Photography Series
description: Explore the art of street photography in a series of guided city walks. Learn how to capture compelling street scenes and candid moments.

title: Night Photography and Light Painting
description: Discover the magic of night photography. This session includes techniques like long exposure and light painting to create stunning images after dark.

title: Photography Basics for Beginners
description: A beginner's guide to photography covering basic concepts, camera operations, and simple techniques to start taking great photos.
